he free videos and other media and use only the shipping benefit. With free two day shipping I now do 90% of my shopping through Amazon. I don't mean 90% of my online shopping...I mean 90% of my TOTAL shopping. Amazon wins. I win. Everyone is happy.You will not regret buying this machine. If you buy an iPad, however, when your kid cracks the screen, they're going to be giving back their allowance for the next 10 years. When looking at small electronic devices, of questionable utility, you shouldn't be thinking about the motorcycle you could have bought for the same price.Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comment



