 for example.2. Physical volume rocker. Somehow a software based rocker is just not useful enough - it takes too long to locate, open and slide.3. The store page should indicate items that you've already bought. When you do searches for items on the store, the resulting lists give no indication on things that you have already bought.4. Camera/Microphone definitely!5. Add more video format playing capability.6. Cellular capability. This along with #4 will make me forget about the iPad completely!At the end of the day, I'm quite happy with my Kindle and do not yet mourn my decision to buy one! :)Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comments (2)

