ements in magazine reading although some of them are already remarkably good. If Amazon continues to keep their eye on the ball, and I think that they will, they will continue to grab more of the marketplace. They have already shown that "tablets", as they currently exist, are good for only certain things and the rest is hype.  More power to them.Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comment

