utton is solved by flipping the Fire upside down.  Power button on top, zero problem.My husband turns on our PC every morning to check The Weather Channel.  Not any more!  There's an app for that!I've used it for about 5 hrs and so far, zero problems.  The touch is VERY sensitive, so caution is required when typing.The Kindle Fire does what I wanted and expected.  I'm still playing with it and learning, but so far, wonderful.Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comments (2)

