indle.  Maybe in future updates this will be allowed.Hope this helps those trying to decide between the Fire and Nook.Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comments (2)

