n be a little errrrrrrrrrrrr.The device is much more responsive since the new software download.  Screen is pretty easy to use.  Does seem to bog down a tad if you happen to be downloading and app and trying to listen to an album while reading a book.  Not horrible just a noted bleep..........I will update this as time and need allow.  We all really like our Fire's.  Amazons ability to help me fill it up make it worth while.  Without the Cloud and the Prime videos I would not own it.note:  customer service with amazon just keeps getting better and better.  I also have two Kindle touches in the house and had a small issue.  They solved it quickly and then even called me back a few hours later to just check up and make sure all was still going well.Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comment

