omputer. The Kindle Fire is nice to use when ready away from home (or at home). The Android app store has tons of apps that are entertaining and handy for a busy mother like myself. A huge plus is that most of these apps are free! If you are thinking about buying a Kindle Fire, consider what you are wanting to use the device for and research other options that might be better for you. Thank you for reading this!Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comment (1)

