 like to load my previous tabs or not.  I'm not sure why this glitch continues to occur, but hopefully it will be fixed with future updates.All in all it's an incredible device for the price.  I would recommend it to anyone looking for a fun side device to take on trips, have for breaks at work or just for everyday use.Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comment (1)

