. Needs even more apps.  Yes, there are a lot, but there could be many more.3. Speakers could be louder.OTHER THOUGHTS1. Would like to have external volume buttons2. Would be nice to be able to insert an SD card, but the cloud makes up for it.3. I've been using it for one month and it goes with me everywhere.  I own an iPad and an iPhone, and I find that I use it more than the other two: The iPad won't fit in my coat pocket, and the iPhone is too small for note taking or watching movies.  Those products are fine, but this one is in some ways better.Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comment

