 SD card to be read on a PC or other device.  It would be a more well-rounded device if the content wasn't so controlled.Help other customers find the most helpful reviews&nbsp;Was this review helpful to you?&nbsp;YesNoReport abuse|PermalinkComment&nbsp;Comments (2)

